      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DARRA SAPPHIRE (1) turned in a modest effort most recently when sixth at this track over 425m behind Flying Petrus (24.91) in a Grade 5. Some good form is emerging from her last run. Better than the latest effort and deserves another chance. COLLINDA POPS (3) racing well without winning, placing at her last four runs. Last start finished 3rd on July 2 over 400m at Warragul behind Sicily beaten 2.25 lengths (23.60) in a Rank Limit - Grade 5. Well placed and gets her chance. PRAWN AND ORDER (7) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (23.48) at Warragul behind Somerton Willow in a Rank Limit - Grade 5. Stalked the pace but found the line strongly. Expecting another good run. VALLETTA PEARL (2) scored last time and can measure up again.",
